Info: 

The fourth game in the Buzz! Junior series sees you take a trip back in time to when 
dinosaurs ruled the Earth. Friendly competition and prehistoric high jinks are the 
order of the day in Buzz! Junior: Dino Den. 
Take control of four cheeky little dinos as they explore the exciting prehistoric world 
around them, wreaking a little havoc along the way.
